'''''Broken Wing''''' is an EP by American [[punk rock]] band [[Alkaline Trio]], released on April 2, 2013 on [[Epitaph Records|Epitaph]] and Heart & Skull. Produced by both [[Bill Stevenson (musician)|Bill Stevenson]] and Jason Livermore, ''Broken Wing'' was recorded during the same sessions that yielded the band's ninth studio album, ''[[My Shame Is True]]'', and was released on the same day. The EP predominantly features songs sung by bassist and vocalist [[Dan Andriano]]. 

Digital deluxe versions of ''My Shame Is True'' include the four songs from ''Broken Wing'' as bonus tracks.<ref>https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/my-shame-is-true-deluxe-edition/id602819984</ref>

